Good deal.  Easy to install.  If your walls are cement behind dry wall no problem but you'll need a cement drill bit.  Measure the back hole inputs of your tv to make sure the holes match before buying this.  Some 32 inch tvs have large rectangular holes versus smaller squared off holes.  The forward tilt is good but there's no way to adjust level so make sure the mount to the wall is correct.
This mount is extremely user friendly, I have mounted flat screens in the past that were much more difficult than this one. Good buy!
