This wall mount came with clearly marked mounting hardware and easy to follow instructions.  It was super easy and was installed in on a matter of minutes.  Some of the other reviews indicated that there was not hardware included for mounting in wood studs, but I found that to be untrue.  There were 2- 4&#34; #4 Black lag bolts included with the hardware package.  So, you don't need to buy any additional hardware if you are mounting in wood studsThe only downside that I have found with this mount is the cable management clips that were included are of little use.  As soon as you put the clips in place along with the desired cables and attempt to swivel the tv, the clips pop off.  I wound up just using zip ties, which have seemed to work quite well.  But for the price of the mount, it was more than worth it.
