I gave this product a 4 star rating. I used it to mount a 40 inch flat screen TV. The bracket is well built, easy to install and has clean lines (no exposed mounting bolts).  An area of the bracket that could be improved is the swivel joint at the back of the TV plate that is used to adjust forward tilt and level of the TV. It works and is sturdy once adjusted but adjustment is by trial and error. Adjustment is achieved by loosening 4 bolts, moving the TV to the desired TV tilt and level and then tightening the bolts while steadying the TV. After tightening the bolts and releasing the TV there is some movement of the joint. Getting the desired tilt and level took several tries.
